== polkit 0.106 ==
polkit changed its rules and actions file format. See the ''polkit'' [[man page]] for more informations. Actions are now in {{Path|/usr/share/polkit-1/actions}}, rules now in {{Path|/usr/share/polkit-1/rules.d}} and {{Path|/etc/polkit-1/rules.d}}.

For the rationale and more informations see [http://davidz25.blogspot.de/2012/06/authorization-rules-in-polkit.html David Zeuthen's blog post].

